{
  "stem": "14212.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until-- until about 13 years of age.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until I was bar mitvah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I know Hebrew very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I loved [INAUDIBLE] and [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Gamurah-- ?] All kind of things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was pretty knowledgeable in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In elementary school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on in the years, especially in the kibbutz, we had a-- a top school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We learned about life, literature and everything what a-- a young man should know about life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I brought myself up to a certain higher standard of educational level.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I lived with it, and I worked this way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Self-educated.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the Germans came, I was in the city, working as a painter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tried to learn a trade which was good for building a country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was working. 1st of September 1939, the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then our city was bombed, and we left the city and went to-- with my future brother-in-law's.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had knowledge of the territory around the city and had a lot of Poles, which he used to deal with.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we went to one of his comrades, and we stayed there a few days until the Germans settled in the city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We sent my little sister, with his daughter, to find out what's what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, as it was, they came back and they said, you know, we've seen the Jews marching and singing the [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Mikvah. ?] She thought that they were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she said the [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Mikvah. ?] And we laughed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had a laugh, but after 10 days in the woods, we went home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As we approached our city, the Germans were waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "All youngsters they called to go to work, to clean up the city from the bombs, shells, from bricks-- clean the city.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
